</p></div></div></div><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-207_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-208_"><ul style="--text-indent:0;--line-spacing:10px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-eSxRXt gEUeuX pf-209_"><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-210_">Always apply sunscreen or wear UPF-rated clothing when going out in the sun.
 
<a href="https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S1743919115010110" target="_self"></a></li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-212_">Avoid any hair removal methods that leave your skin irritated or cause ingrown hairs. 
. 
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-214_">If you shave, make sure to do so gently, always using a cushioning shaving cream and a sharp razor that’s less likely to irritate.
 
</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-216_">Exfoliate regularly to prevent dead skin buildup and to encourage your skin to renew itself in a healthy way. Our <u><a href="/products/body-exfoliator" target="_self">Evertone Body Exfoliator</a></u> includes coffee powder and oils to keep your skin looking firm, supple, and smooth while also helping to reduce the look of cellulite.  
 </li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-218_">Find ways to reduce rubbing and friction against your skin by wearing soft, comfortable clothing or using barrier creams. 
  
 </li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-aaqME gaxjKK pf-220_">Moisturize regularly to keep your skin strong and fortified. Look for creams like our <u><a href="/products/anti-cellulite-cream-body-shaper" target="_self">Evertone Body Shaper</a></u>, which features soothing green tea and caffeine to keep dark spot-causing irritation at bay. 
 
  
